result.name: car-parking-account-cheltenham
result.notes:
This dataset contains an annual summary of the car parking account from Cheltenham Borough Council. 

These include a breakdown of the income and expenditure on the parking account and a breakdown of how the authority has spent any surplus on its parking account.

Cheltenham Borough Council’s car parking account only relates to the off-street car parks that it owns; it does not collect for, or enforce any on-street parking. 

Expenditure includes cost for the provision and maintenance of designated parking places by the local authority. Information about the council’s car parks including location, number of parking bays, number of disabled parking spaces and charges can be found on our dedicated parking information page on our website.
result.title: Car parking account from Cheltenham Borough Council
